name: Turn On, Tune In, Glitch Out

metadata.name: Sunset Blvd GlitchScape
metadata.description:
Introducing "Sunset Boulevard GlitchScape," the first NFT from the "Turn On, Tune In, Glitch Out" collection that opens the doors of perception to a visionary glitch experience of 1970s Sunset Boulevard. As you embark on this mind-expanding journey, you'll encounter a blonde actress, the quintessence of Hollywood allure, captured in a transcendental dance of digital distortion.

As she glitches and shimmers, the legendary Sunset Boulevard becomes a surreal dreamscape, pulsating with psychedelic energy. This NFT invites you to dive into the depths of your consciousness, exploring the transformative power of glitch art and the enchanting spirit of 1970s Los Angeles.

"Sunset Boulevard GlitchScape" is an ode to the boundless beauty that arises when nostalgia and cutting-edge glitch converge. So, turn on, tune in, and immerse yourself in this psychedelic glitch of a bygone era.
